'''Erik Myers''' is an American comedian, actor, and writer.
== Early life == Myers grew up in [[Columbia, Maryland]] and began his comedy career at the age of 18 at Winchester's Pub in Baltimore.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uproarcomedycd.com/shop/erik-myers-basket-case/|title=Erik Myers â€“ "Basket Case" |publisher=Uproar Entertainment}}</ref> In 2005 he won the "Funniest Person in Baltimore" contest.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://comedyunderground.com/erik-myers-recording-new-comedy-album-comedy-underground/|title=Erik Myers recording at Comedy Underground|date=17 July 2014|publisher=Comedy Underground}}</ref> Myers later moved to Florida where he was named 2011 Florida's Funniest Comedian.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://floridasfunny.com|title=Florida's Funny|publisher=}}</ref>{{failed verification|date=January 2017}}
== Career ==
Myers is based in [[Los Angeles]], [[California]] where he's a paid regular at the world-famous ''Comedy Store'' in Hollywood.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://standuptalk.com/19-comedians-get-passed-at-the-comedy-store-for-2014/|title=19 Comedians Get Passed at the Comedy Store for 2014 |date=7 August 2015|publisher=StandUpTalk}}</ref> He has appeared on "''Gotham City Live''", "''Laughs''" on the Fox Network, and performed his 1-hour special "''Dopeless Romantic''" for [[Hulu]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ticketfly.com/event/1401871-erik-myers-as-seen-on-las-vegas/|title=Erik Myers as seen on Showtime, Laughs and Live at Gotham - Ticket sales site|date=January 12, 2017|website=www.ticketfly.com}}</ref> He has appeared on "''Andrew Dice Clay Presents''", "''The Blue Show''" on Showtime, and "''Comics Unleashed with Byron Allen''".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.laughfactory.com/erikmyers|title=The Erik Myers Channel |publisher=Laugh Factory Comedy Network}}</ref> Myers is the co-creator of the animated cartoon "''Court Ordered''", loosely based on his life with characters voiced by many fellow notable comedians.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://courtorderedcartoon.com|title=Court Ordered|website=courtorderedcartoon.com}}</ref>
